    "body" : "<p>If you get  an exception for : Invalid column type</p>\n\n<p>Please use <code>getNamedParameterJdbcTemplate()</code> instead of <code>getJdbcTemplate()</code></p>\n\n<pre><code> List&lt;Foo&gt; foo = getNamedParameterJdbcTemplate().query(\"SELECT * FROM foo WHERE a IN (:ids)\",parameters,\n getRowMapper());\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note that the second two arguments are swapped around. </p>\n"
